== Tlhokomelo ya dihutshane ==
* O TLHOPHA JANG TSE DI NAMAGADI, DIPHOKO LE DIPHELEFU TSE DI KA GO DIRELANG SENTLE.
Go tlhopha dihutshane tsa letsalo ke thulaganyo e morui a tshwanetseng  go e dira gangwe le gape, ka go dira jalo go tla thusa morui go rua dihutshane tse di nang le boleng. O ka ela thoko tse, mo thophong ya gago boleng jwa nama, letsalo le bokete.
